EN: We need to select a sofa that suits our home decoration.

ZH: 妈妈正在挑选新的家具来更新客厅的装饰。
EN: Mom is choosing new furniture to update the living room decor.

ZH: 我去了五家不同的超市，才最终挑选购买了食材。
EN: I went to five different supermarkets before finally selecting and buying the ingredients.

